RomType.description:
ROM chip type

Supported retro ROM chip types with their pinouts and characteristics.
Includes mask ROMs (23xx series) and EPROMs (27xx series).

# Examples

```
use onerom_config::rom::RomType;

let rom = RomType::Rom2364;
assert_eq!(rom.size_bytes(), 8192);
assert_eq!(rom.rom_pins(), 24);
assert_eq!(rom.num_addr_lines(), 13);
```
